snippet: The woman stabbed and lightly wounded an Israeli man at a hitchhiking stop before she was shot and wounded by Israeli soldiers at the scene.
abstract: Palestinian woman stabs Israeli man at hitchhiking stop in West Bank and is then shot and wounded by Israeli soldiers in the area; incident is latest in wave of attacks against Israelis.
lead_paragraph: The woman stabbed and lightly wounded an Israeli man at a hitchhiking stop before she was shot and wounded by Israeli soldiers at the scene.

headline.main: Palestinian Woman Attacked Israeli Man in West Bank
headline.print_headline: West Bank: Palestinian Assailant Wounded by Soldiers
